Enum CODATag

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CODATag>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CODATag>

    public enum CODATag
extends java.lang.Enum<CODATag>
    This enum specifies values associated with tags used in CODA online components.
    Author:
    timmer

      Trigger bank from ROC with 32 bit timestamps.
      RAW_TRIGGER_TS_BIG
      Trigger bank from ROC with 64 bit timestamps.
